    "slug": "smart-kitchen-appliances-2026",
    "title": "Smart Kitchen Appliances: Is Smart Worth It in 2026?",
    "excerpt": "From AI-powered fridges to WiFi-enabled ovens, we test the latest smart kitchen tech and tell you what's actually worth the investment.",
    "category": "Guide",
    "date": "Mar 10, 2026",
